divs: Sighting Detailsi was watching tv as i noticed a commercial of a clown majic act. He was showing a bottle of pinesol with a wand and how stains dissapeared majically. After seeing this i went across the street and bought some fabrisolv, and polished my computer. I remember needing something from my purse as i noticed that my wallet was not there. I recall thinking that maybe my wallet had telaported somewhere after using the fabrisolv Two weeeks later i recieved a fedex as the package had indeed my returned wallet. The return address was from the store, bath and beyond. I knew i did not shop there, so how did this happen? Maybe my walllet teleported to a ufo they may have. ALl my credit cards were there, even my laundry card was there, and only some cash under $20 was missing...unfortunatly my expensive alienware computer stopped working after using this fluid cleaner. My disc drive compleatly no longer reconized its own hardware.
